        <abstract> 
<p>Describes subscription for Torbitt [to continue potato experiments]. Would dislike writing to any paper, but Hensleigh [Wedgwood] and Erasmus [Darwin] advise CD to write to the <hi rend="italic">Times</hi>.</p> 
